thread.title: ‘Rural Olympics’ attracts stuntmen, performers from across India

title: ‘Rural Olympics’ attracts stuntmen, performers from across India
text:
‘Rural Olympics’ attracts stuntmen, performers from across India 1:09pm IST - 01:28 
Thousands gather for the annual ‘Rural Olympics’ in India’s northern Punjab state where participants take part in everything from traditional athletics, to feats of strength and tractor racing. Ashraf Fahim reports
